data.description: Welcome to 851 Laurel Ln, a lovely end unit townhome situated in the highly sought-after town of La Plata, Maryland. This exceptional home offers a perfect blend of modern living, comfort, and convenience, making it an irresistible opportunity.   Step inside and be greeted by a split foyer. The main/lower level features spacious living areas, including a separate dining area perfect for hosting gatherings, a cozy family room where you can unwind after a long day and a half bathroom perfect for guests to use. Natural light pours through the new windows, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. The kitchen has been tastefully updated with brand new stainless steel appliances and ample cabinet storage. On the upper level, this home boasts 3 bedrooms and full bath. You can access the bathroom from the master bedroom and hallway. It has brand new carpet and new flooring throughout. Outside, the spacious backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment.  Additional features of this home include a 2 car driveway, providing convenient parking. The location also offers proximity to a wide array of amenities, including shopping, dining, entertainment, and a vibrant community atmosphere. No HOA! Property eligible for USDA, 100% financing. Contact your local lender. Seller offering one year home warranty. Schedule a showing today! This one won't last long. Property being sold As-Is.  If anyone is ill, has flu-like symptoms or recently been exposed to Covid-19 please do not show. Please follow all CDC Covid-19 guidelines when showing property. Thank you.
